Package com.telenav.kivakit.configuration.settings.deployment

Class DeploymentSet

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.kernel.messaging.broadcasters.Multicaster
com.telenav.kivakit.kernel.messaging.repeaters.BaseRepeater
com.telenav.kivakit.configuration.settings.deployment.DeploymentSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
Receiver<Transmittable>, Transmitter<Transmittable>, NamedObject, PackagePathed, Broadcaster, Listener, Repeater, Transceiver
public class DeploymentSet extends BaseRepeater
A set of Deployment objects, each being a set of configuration objects. Deployments can be added to the set from a folder with addDeploymentsIn(Folder). A switch parser to select a deployment from the command line can be retrieved with SwitchParser.deployment(DeploymentSet).
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
See Also:
Deployment, Settings
